Catalog





Request A CatalogIf you are looking for versatile seating, a sofa and loveseat set are the perfect combination of style and function. The sofa can seat anywhere from 3 to 5 and the loveseat can fit two comfortably. So you can easily seat 5 to 8 with a sofa loveseat pair.
You don’t need to compromise on style either. Get a leather sofa and love seat and mix it with other fabrics and items in your room to make a statement. Or have your leather loveseat sofa set be the focal point and design your room around them. With Bassett’s large selection of sofas and love seats, getting the exact look you are going for is simple!
For a traditional parlor look, our sofa and loveseat is a good choice. With a camel-back frame and optional turned legs or skirt, it is both functional and fashionable. Or for something more regal, the leather loveseat and sofa set is a good choice. With plush, hand rubbed leather, this sofa and loveseat set has a classic old world flair to upgrade any room.
Check out Bassett Furniture’s selection of sofas and love seats! Or, shop by sofa and loveseat style and fabric.Related ProductsSofa Recliner SofasFeatures & Design TipsSofa and Loveseat Layout IdeasLiving Room Design Help from HGTV





