Catalog





Bedroom FurnitureView Our CatalogEveryone needs a place where you can get away after a long, hard days’ work.  With Basset’s wide selection of bedroom furniture and bedroom furniture sets, you can create the perfect place to unwind and rest.  Basset offers the finest in luxury bedroom furniture and our highly skilled staff can help you find the perfect bedroom set to suit your taste and price point. We offer everything from contemporary to traditional bedroom furniture, along with everything in between.
Consider a theme or period before you begin your bedroom furniture shopping. Do you prefer a contemporary or traditional look? Rustic, modern or cottage? When looking for individual bedroom furniture pieces, this is an imperative. It will affect the colors and finishes you choose. Make sure you measure the room before you floor plan and remember that you’ll be living with your new bedroom furniture every day so don’t forget about functionality. For example, you may wish to choose furniture that provides additional storage space.
Choose from complete, matching bedroom furniture sets to individual bedroom furniture pieces, depending on your preference and budget. While mixing and matching bedroom furniture can be an enjoyable experience for some, others may prefer the convenience of purchasing and entire matching bedroom set. Either way, a Bassett associate is ready and able to assist you.
We spend more time in the bedroom than any other room in the home. And while our beds are the most important element to this room, don’t overlook the importance of bedroom furniture such as nightstands, wall mirrors, armoires, dressers and other accessories in making your living space comfortable. Shop from our wide selection of bedroom accessories and accent pieces to make your bedroom space complete.
Let’s not forget mattresses. Whether you prefer a very firm mattress or a mattress that contours to your body shape and type, you’ll find the one that best suits you at Bassett. We offer a wide variety of top manufacturers such as Sealy, Serta and Sterns & Foster, just to name a few. You’ll find plush mattresses, pillow tops – you name it, priced to move and within your budget. Additionally, we carry designer bedding including mattress covers, quilts, blankets, and throw pillows in colors and patterns that are sure to match your bedroom decor.
Finally, Bassett offers a great selection of decorative wall art for your bedroom, living room or anywhere within your home. Color alone can reflect and attitude or make a bold statement, so consider the type of environment you wish to create before selecting wall art. Remember that pastels create a peaceful environment while hot colors create and entirely different kind of feng shui or vibe.
Our bedroom furniture features classic looks that never go out of style. If you are into more modern style, we have the perfect combination of casual, elegant, and natural looking bedroom-furniture.  Whatever you are looking for Basset furniture can help create the look you envision. Come in and visit us in our stores to look at the extensive bedroom furniture collections we carry.Related ProductsAccent FurnitureNightstandsFeatures & Design TipsBedroom TipsContemporary Bedroom IdeasModern Bedroom Ideas





