Catalog





Dining TablesView Our CatalogWhen it is time to sit down and have a meal with the family, you should do it with style and comfort.  One of the easiest ways to accomplish this is to add brand new dining tables in your dining area.  When you are choosing a new dining room table, many different factors are involved.  The size, style and look are all important elements. 
Bassett Furniture offers many great deals and designs so that you can find perfect dining room tables and dining room sets. If you are seeking a more contemporary feel, our tables fit nicely in any modern kitchen and seats two easily.  With a round glass top, you can maintain an open feel in your dining area.  Dining tables and sets are available in multiple sizes, so you can choose what best fits your lifestyle.  
Shop Bassett's large selection of dining tables here. Or, browse our dining chair, kitchen table, and dining room sets.Related ProductsDining Tables and ChairsGathering TablesFeatures & Design TipsDining Room IdeasDining Room Inspirations





